{"tid":224533,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想host一個web application，有無好介紹？","createTime":"2017-05-01T06:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T22:30:41.000Z","uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"640e3c3f6f88cfd54673dcb32cbf2d6a6efdab64","tid":224533,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"想要一個linux vm，會host個web server，mysql同smtp server，筆直每月1000以內，初步了解過pac hosting同go daddy，但唔係好知點揀，有無巴打有好介紹？"},{"pid":"bdf72c4d7e120c1ef64c4fe4fbc277e0b37de1be","tid":224533,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想要一個linux vm，會host個web server，mysql同smtp server，筆直每月1000以內，初步了解過pac hosting同go daddy，但唔係好知點揀，有無巴打有好介紹？</blockquote><br />\n有無睇過linode/aws嗰啲？"},{"pid":"7b072395d2816ce9c40ec55a4ab047cd4903ecd6","tid":224533,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想要一個linux vm，會host個web server，mysql同smtp server，筆直每月1000以內，初步了解過pac hosting同go daddy，但唔係好知點揀，有無巴打有好介紹？</blockquote><br />\n有無睇過linode/aws嗰啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過aws ec2個free vm，但一來aws係香港無data center，二黎按用量收費"},{"pid":"fe5c95acad5f89f96aa54f002efa1631df396f48","tid":224533,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"digital ocean"},{"pid":"ac4da98f36b00202e5a86cc61e16bf1a0a07db32","tid":224533,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"on9.hosting"},{"pid":"864436be4a8f2b1e55f82faf5403a5576f611fc3","tid":224533,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"Raspberry Pi&nbsp;3b x2"},{"pid":"a185d8c9153fc105d8a0c98eb6cf46fc0c745b26","tid":224533,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想要一個linux vm，會host個web server，mysql同smtp server，筆直每月1000以內，初步了解過pac hosting同go daddy，但唔係好知點揀，有無巴打有好介紹？</blockquote><br />\n有無睇過linode/aws嗰啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過aws ec2個free vm，但一來aws係香港無data center，二黎按用量收費</blockquote><br />\nAzure 有HK DC <br />\n二來compute engine d vm 係有monthly cost, static 數黎，按量收費只係話你知最低可以一分鐘/一小時咁收姐。"},{"pid":"48326facae25bce085b11933902fa77aa6dab5b5","tid":224533,"uid":78236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想要一個linux vm，會host個web server，mysql同smtp server，筆直每月1000以內，初步了解過pac hosting同go daddy，但唔係好知點揀，有無巴打有好介紹？</blockquote><br />\n有無睇過linode/aws嗰啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過aws ec2個free vm，但一來aws係香港無data center，二黎按用量收費</blockquote><br />\n就算斷鐘計, 你個server長開咪即係比月費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d斷鐘計+monthly cap, 佢個hourly charge大約都係monthly cap / 28 / 34<br />\n如果你用serverless又唔同玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋香港冇data center, 新加坡同日本都好似唔錯"},{"pid":"ebea1467e9631cbf4c28e5bd9e4e50f89ff504f4","tid":224533,"uid":75575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"Aws新加坡啦，月費黎講好似300到？nano既話"},{"pid":"50e38e3c15525f5dd74b7bd83174d22830135bf6","tid":224533,"uid":75575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Aws新加坡啦，月費黎講好似300到？nano既話</blockquote><br />\nMedium 先啱，nano一個月40蚊"},{"pid":"366fee62272aa878defc594e31cea1bfd1a9a668","tid":224533,"uid":2357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"Azure點睇，有無人用過，google app呢？"},{"pid":"e0550a77ac0cf896418c672dffe71269c51ec32d","tid":224533,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Azure點睇，有無人用過，google app呢？</blockquote><br />\n兩個都有用<br />\n速度黎講azure/gc 唔錯<br />\n但azure 個portal on9咗啲"},{"pid":"038a4e314a86a46209bc4a1a0607407ab2784627","tid":224533,